---
title: Sticky Crusted Tofu with Jasmine Rice, Teriyaki Mushrooms & Cucumber Pickle
description: We love a good Tofu with Rice and Mushrooms and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sticky-crusted-tofu-83a4b4f6-3309ed82.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sticky-crusted-tofu-5d08ba47a79ba0001012559c-5c241f0b.pdf
nutrition:
  calories: 594 kcal
