  sodium: 3 g
  serving size: 491
servings: 2
time required: 40 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/sticky-crusted-tofu-5d08ba47a79ba0001012559c
author: Mimi Morley
course: main course
cuisine: Asian
